'''The Ambarkanta''' is the fifth chapter of ''[[The Shaping of Middle-earth]]''. The chapter includes the text "Ambarkanta: The Shape of the World" (attributed to [[Rúmil (elf of Tirion)|Rúmil]]) and the associated [[Ambarkanta maps|''Ambarkanta'' maps]].

Developed during the 1930s, according to [[Christopher Tolkien]], the Ambarkanta represents the "next phase" of the cosmology after the earlier world described in the ''[[Book of Lost Tales]]''.<ref>{{LT1|IIIn}}</ref>
